headline: Truist Lifts Price Target on Weyerhaeuser Company (WY) Despite Near-Term Volume Dip
summary: We recently published an article titled 9 Best Lumber Stocks to Invest in Now. On February 2, Truist raised its price target on Weyerhaeuser Company (NYSE:WY) to $29 from $28 while maintaining a Hold rating. The firm noted that lighter fourth-quarter volumes were largely timing-related, as the company accelerated harvest activity into the summer ahead […]
